    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.03352.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">431 Stevens Street</name>
                    <name type="place" rend="right">Camden New Jersey U S America<ptr target="loc.04038_n1"/></name>
               </dateline>
                <salute>My dear Wm Harrison Riley</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>Your letter has reach'd me here &#38; I thank you for your affectionate warmth &#38; appreciation.</p>
            
            <p>I have long wanted to do myself the pleasure of sending a book of mine to Mr Ruskin, &#38; I have sent one&#8212;also a couple of photographs&#8212;directed to him, to your care, by the same mail with this&#8212;same address&#8212;</p>
            
            <p>Please send me word soon as they reach you &#38; are delivered to Mr R&#8212;</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
